      "text": "Bernard Berek.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met him [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] '64 or '65-- no, what I am talking? '36?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
